{"type": "article", "id": 50732, "title": "谭维维推出个人形象识别系统，工商银行做了个 Gif 广告 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-03-02T04:08:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 14153, "name": "谭维维"}, {"id": 1036, "name": "耐克"}, {"id": 329, "name": "宝洁"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180302115603YaHUDMiCxk09tWmp.png", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 10.0px 0.0px; line-height: 23.0px; font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 10.0px 0.0px; line-height: 23.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 10.0px 0.0px; line-height: 23.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 19.0px} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 10.0px 0.0px; line-height: 23.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 10.0px 0.0px; line-height: 23.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 14.0px} p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p9 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 19.0px} span.s1 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s2 {font: 18.0px Georgia; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939} span.s5 {font: 16.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 16.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none} span.s8 {font: 14.0px Arial; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/only-runners-can-save-the-world-in-nikes-star-studded-spin-on-disaster-movies/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>创意代理 Must Be Something 给 Nike 拍了个广告</b></a>，讲的是通过跑步拯救世界，科比、Kevin Hart 等一众明星出演。但看起来似乎有点尴尬。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=d0563qelf78&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26076.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>FILA 和 VOGUE 合作拍摄了一支广告</b></a>，代言人陈坤在 FILA 的品牌起源地意大利小镇比耶拉参与拍摄，演绎了一个关于挚爱的冒险故事——为什么印象中最近陈坤拍的广告都一个样？<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=m0561vq2rem&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/articles/43879.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>谭维维工作室发布了一套《谭维维个人形象识别系统》</b></a>，包括 Logo、专属手势、标签化系统，还有一堆谭维维的周边。她不是第一个这么做的明星，早年的田震、成龙都有个人视觉形象设计。从社交平台上的粉丝反馈来看，果然喜欢她，就是喜欢她的一切啊。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302114810VZYIzFSKR012PEJM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.122222\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302114819yOFUqw9Z7GkioNaB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.309259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26054.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>工商银行也做了一组数字营销</b></a>，为了推广春节期间工银银联信用卡的境外消费返现活动。GIF 的美工看起来还不错，传统金融巨头们在社交网络上的营销越来越活跃了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302134018RzjMr4Z7DpECebqx.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.778333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><b><a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/p-g-slashed-digital-ad-spending-by-another-100-million-1519915621\" rel=\"nofollow\">宝洁去年共减少了 2 亿元的数字广告支出</a></b>，数据显示他们减少最多的投放平台是 Google 和 YouTube。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/why-does-pizza-hut-want-an-nfl-sponsorship-when-papa-johns-doesnt/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Papa John's 和 NFL 结束赞助合约后，必胜客接手了</b></a>。根据统计，37% 的人喜欢在看橄榄球的时候吃披萨。不过这项交易也可能存在风险，Papa John's 曾指责 NFL 未能管理好联盟，包括球员在奏响时下跪等争议行为，伤害了联盟品牌价值。</p><p class=\"\">题图来源：数英网</p>"}